### MiniTransfer API - fichier de test HTTP
### Compatible avec l'extension "REST Client" (VS Code) ou le client HTTP d'IntelliJ.
### Astuce : executez "Register" ou "Login", copiez le "token" renvoye dans la variable @token ci-dessous.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = COLLER_LE_TOKEN_ICI

### 1. Inscription (cree un compte + portefeuille a 10 000 FCFA)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Dupont",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "phone": "+237600000001",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 1bis. Inscription d'un second utilisateur (destinataire)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Martin",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "phone": "+237600000002",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 2. Connexion (retourne un token JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 3. Consulter le solde du portefeuille (authentifie)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Effectuer un transfert vers Bob
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "bob@example.com",
  "amount": 2500
}

### 5. Consulter l'historique des transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/transfers/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### --- Cas d'erreur ---

### Montant superieur au solde -> 400 INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "bob@example.com",
  "amount": 999999999
}

### Transfert vers soi-meme -> 400 SELF_TRANSFER
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "alice@example.com",
  "amount": 1000
}

### Destinataire inexistant -> 404 RECIPIENT_NOT_FOUND
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "ghost@example.com",
  "amount": 1000
}

### Montant negatif -> 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "bob@example.com",
  "amount": -50
}

### Sans token -> 401 UNAUTHENTICATED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance
